version_description:
The app is no longer letter-boxed on iPhone5.
The background images and a few button images have been updated for retina display.

The app is no longer letter-boxed on iPhone5.
The background images and a few button images have been updated for retina display.

The new Microcell application can now be used better by the visually challenged.
•It is 64-bit enabled.
•Password masking issue in the login screen is fixed.
•The application now has better Address Book (Contacts) matching. Your address book is used to simplify the process of adding mobile numbers to the User List through quicker and easier way to match contacts.
